\begin_layout Itemize
Probability 
\begin_inset Formula $P:\mathcal{F}\mapsto\left[0,1\right]$
\end_inset

 is a function such that: (i) 
\begin_inset Formula $P\left(A\right)\geq0$
\end_inset

 for all 
\begin_inset Formula $A\in\mathcal{F}$
\end_inset

